> Each day youâ€™d just need to run `aws sso login --sso-session <my-sso>`
In this example, what is <my-sso> supposed to be? our email address?

It would be whatever you set the session name to when setting up the CLI. I wrote a doc on that which you can find on the wiki here: https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IT/pages/1947435025/Setting+up+SSO+for+the+AWS+CLI
